{"tid":1215590,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【速龍淆底】拖散仔出嚟擋，可憐個散仔震晒。","createTime":"2019-06-13T07:37:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T09:01:08.000Z","uid":191462,"like":45,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f0a47a7809ccfc4ec02e751956d968db0052e223","tid":1215590,"uid":191462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T07:37:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3bjdCyr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3bjdCyr.png&h=74ab8caf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當時各位無辜嘅群眾應該喺添美道嗰頭俾人火力壓制梗，希望你哋冇受太大傷害。<br />\n<br />\n由於太危險嘅關係，我喺立法會旁喺佢哋準備行動時，從佢哋身邊行過咗去佢哋大後方，即防線後面 &mdash; 立法會門口同龍和道一帶。<br />\n<br />\n不過話時話，唔知點解出其地容易，呢下自己都呆咗。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">我可能係全日唯一一個無需衝擊，one man army咁就突破咗警方防線嘅人</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後喺到坐咗兩個鐘同班防暴你眼望我眼。<br />\n<br />\n當其時現場得返幾條友，之後走剩我一個，我喺電話確保晒在場朋友安全後我都走咗。<br />\n<br />\n咁喺我同佢哋互相對望同望佢哋欺負途人時，有一個速龍右手持警棍；左手持散仔（加盾）一步一步咁行埋嚟。<br />\n<br />\n可能佢怕我識影分身突然變堆人出嚟突襲佢掛～ <br />\n<br />\nWhatever啦～<br />\n<br />\n之後佢見冇乜危險就推走個散仔叫佢返入去。<br />\n然後就落指令叫班防暴call佢架車出嚟。<br />\n<br />\n-故事完結- <br />\n<br />\n利申：冇犯任何刑事，所以唔怕俾人拉。<br />\n<br />\n但勿相認！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6cd6d3ded9c88cdd13ae5bc85007d4c8f40fb41","tid":1215590,"uid":40470,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T07:41:12.000Z","msg":"書名：毒撚零存在感的故事"},{"pid":"e0f6970a2837558016035bcd0b4579b879f49b22","tid":1215590,"uid":236368,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T07:41:25.000Z","msg":"真心笑咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c71481a783bcbc0be32fe3817d8c1e86298e2e2","tid":1215590,"uid":16844,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T07:42:07.000Z","msg":"個速龍右手持警棍；左手持散仔（加盾）一步一步咁行埋嚟"},{"pid":"aeeef85377b1c9a5a78f5cda18282bd54d096b27","tid":1215590,"uid":58335,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T07:42:38.000Z","msg":"放狗係咁上下"},{"pid":"04628da84044d4c729dfa6ed51e7d2abef401991","tid":1215590,"uid":188362,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T07:46:53.000Z","msg":"關乜事 <br />\n人地個陣係盾行先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ac80017b78808bfde1dee1b3d4d84f264579581","tid":1215590,"uid":38030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T07:49:17.000Z","msg":"做差佬同做cctvb慘過做狗，做狗俾人打主人都會幫你出頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c700dbdcc48504a21ef5ebe5aeb11aee3b07fc3","tid":1215590,"uid":191462,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T08:02:00.000Z","msg":"班防暴行出嚟準備列陣時，前排白衫madam對住佢哋叫：企好啲！<br />\n我以為小學集隊。"},{"pid":"081be7e76b1bf9cf4fe49f65586ef4f2d5a7c54c","tid":1215590,"uid":191462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"04628da84044d4c729dfa6ed51e7d2abef401991","tid":1215590,"uid":188362,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T07:46:53.000Z","msg":"關乜事 <br />\n人地個陣係盾行先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T08:03:26.000Z","msg":"錯重點，我冇話佢陣法唔啱純粹係唔知佢驚乜。"},{"pid":"8534c3299b482b7f4ad669a480a5290c95169aba","tid":1215590,"uid":191462,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a6cd6d3ded9c88cdd13ae5bc85007d4c8f40fb41","tid":1215590,"uid":40470,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T07:41:12.000Z","msg":"書名：毒撚零存在感的故事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T08:05:16.000Z","msg":"連我呢啲毒撚都夠膽企出嚟上前線。師兄你係咪好似Captain Marvel咁周圍飛拯救星球所以唔得閒出嚟？"},{"pid":"ed38e20fca28dcf9cd662239c2ed9cd8cabfbbf2","tid":1215590,"uid":174767,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T08:09:49.000Z","msg":"FULLGEAR, 隻揪都驚仲要吹雞？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c989b701c384c1ca8ab228ab3ced6d9c4db1406","tid":1215590,"uid":165840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c